<section xmlns="http://xml.house.gov/schemas/uslm/1.0" style="-uslm-lc:I80" id="id0d93eb5c-2931-11f1-afae-ea39e71ac6b0" identifier="/us/usc/t52/s20502"><num value="20502">§ 20502.</num><heading> Definitions</heading>
<chapeau style="-uslm-lc:I11" class="indent0">As used in this chapter—</chapeau><paragraph style="-uslm-lc:I12" class="indent1" id="id0d93eb5d-2931-11f1-afae-ea39e71ac6b0" identifier="/us/usc/t52/s20502/1"><num value="1">(1)</num><content> the term “election” has the meaning stated in <ref href="/us/usc/t52/s30101/1">section 30101(1) of this title</ref>;</content>
</paragraph>
<paragraph style="-uslm-lc:I12" class="indent1" id="id0d93eb5e-2931-11f1-afae-ea39e71ac6b0" identifier="/us/usc/t52/s20502/2"><num value="2">(2)</num><content> the term “Federal office” has the meaning stated in <ref href="/us/usc/t52/s30101/3">section 30101(3) of this title</ref>;</content>
</paragraph>
<paragraph style="-uslm-lc:I12" class="indent1" id="id0d93eb5f-2931-11f1-afae-ea39e71ac6b0" identifier="/us/usc/t52/s20502/3"><num value="3">(3)</num><content> the term “motor vehicle driver’s license” includes any personal identification document issued by a State motor vehicle authority;</content>
</paragraph>
<paragraph style="-uslm-lc:I12" class="indent1" id="id0d965c60-2931-11f1-afae-ea39e71ac6b0" identifier="/us/usc/t52/s20502/4"><num value="4">(4)</num><content> the term “State” means a State of the United States and the District of Columbia; and</content>
</paragraph>
<paragraph style="-uslm-lc:I12" class="indent1" id="id0d965c61-2931-11f1-afae-ea39e71ac6b0" identifier="/us/usc/t52/s20502/5"><num value="5">(5)</num><content> the term “voter registration agency” means an office designated under <ref href="/us/usc/t52/s20506/a/1">section 20506(a)(1) of this title</ref> to perform voter registration activities.</content>
</paragraph>
<sourceCredit id="id0d965c62-2931-11f1-afae-ea39e71ac6b0">(<ref href="/us/pl/103/31/s3">Pub. L. 103–31, § 3</ref>, <date date="1993-05-20">May 20, 1993</date>, <ref href="/us/stat/107/77">107 Stat. 77</ref>.)</sourceCredit>
<notes type="uscNote" id="id0d965c63-2931-11f1-afae-ea39e71ac6b0">
<note style="-uslm-lc:I74" role="crossHeading" topic="editorialNotes" id="id0d965c64-2931-11f1-afae-ea39e71ac6b0"><heading class="centered"><b>Editorial Notes</b></heading></note>
<note style="-uslm-lc:I76" topic="codification" id="id0d965c65-2931-11f1-afae-ea39e71ac6b0"><heading class="centered smallCaps">Codification</heading>
<p style="-uslm-lc:I21" class="indent0">Section was formerly classified to <ref href="/us/usc/t42/s1973gg–1">section 1973gg–1 of Title 42</ref>, The Public Health and Welfare, prior to editorial reclassification and renumbering as this section.</p>
</note>
</notes>
